{"data":[{"date":"15:05 20/07","title":"Anh trai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante \u0111\u1ed9t t\u1eed ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/anh-trai-tien-ve-kante-dot-tu-ngay-truoc-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 anh trai N\u2019Golo Kante \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9t t\u1eed ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo t\u1edd Orange (Ph\u00e1p), anh trai c\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a N\u2019Golo Kante l\u00e0 Niama \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9t t\u1eed v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tim m\u1ea1ch ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec l\u00fd do n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1ea1i Nga. Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng c\u1ea3 c\u01a1n \u0111au d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh trai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9t t\u1eed ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Anh trai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9t t\u1eed ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/kante-the-hien-su-khiem-nhuong-khi-nhac-toi-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia \u0111\u00ecnh Kante \u0111\u00f4ng con. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 4 ch\u1ecb em g\u00e1i v\u00e0 3 anh em trai kh\u00e1c. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, anh \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i \u0111au m\u1ea5t Niama \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi\u00a0 N\u2019Golo Kante ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng n\u1ed7i \u0111au m\u1ea5t \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft ru\u1ed9t th\u1ecbt. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t cha t\u1eeb n\u0103m 11 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 tu\u1ed5i th\u01a1 r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ban \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Kante c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u00fap gia \u0111\u00ecnh anh \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c. Ch\u1ec9 khi chuy\u1ec3n sang Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Leicester City v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Chelsea, Kante m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u0103m lo cho c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Kante ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1eddi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec1n l\u00e0nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n nh\u00fat nh\u00e1t. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 y\u00eau m\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4422","checkdouble":"191668"},{"date":"15:07 20/07","title":"Chelsea ra m\u1eaft m\u1eabu \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0ng r\u1ef1c cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/chelsea-ra-mat-mau-ao-dau-vang-ruc-cho-mua-giai-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng m\u1eabu \u00e1o s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi (2018-19).</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">M\u00e0u v\u00e0ng l\u00e0 t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho b\u1ed9 trang ph\u1ee5c s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19. M\u00e0u \u00e1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Blues s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1963, sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 70 c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Chelsea s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2014-15. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y London \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Jose Mourinho. Nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t Nike tin t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc n\u00e0y s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho The Blues \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHazard, Kante, Alonso, Cahill, Willian v\u00e0 n\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Fran Kirby l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong ch\u00f9m \u1ea3nh ra m\u1eaft \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Chelsea. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Hazard, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Chelsea tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 28/7 t\u1edbi, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Inter Milan thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/180720_145346_347.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/180720_145325_416.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/180720_145202_686.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/180720_145146_802.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/180720_145130_801.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/180720_145049_768.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4421","checkdouble":"191670"},{"date":"15:26 20/07","title":"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rakitic th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n b\u00ean gia \u0111\u00ecnh sau World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/tien-ve-rakitic-thu-gian-ben-gia-dinh-sau-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4420","checkdouble":"191672"},{"date":"15:50 20/07","title":"\u00c1o \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 c\u00f3 m\u00e0u ... h\u1ed3ng","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/20/ao-dau-san-khach-cua-mu-o-mua-giai-201819-co-mau-hong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Khi c\u00e1c C\u0110V M.U v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u01b0ng \u00fd v\u1edbi \u00e1o s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 th\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, m\u00f4t C\u0110V t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan ch\u1ee5p l\u1ea1i m\u1eabu \u00e1o s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, trang ph\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a M.U d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0u... h\u1ed3ng ph\u1ea5n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u00e3ng Adidas g\u1eedi l\u1eddi tri \u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean m\u1ee5c \"Football Pink\" \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in tr\u00ean gi\u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u00ean t\u1edd b\u00e1o Manchester Evening News.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/mu_ao_dau3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ed9 c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y l\u00e0 109,95 b\u1ea3ng. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \"m\u1ec1m\" h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua trang ph\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a M.U. \u0110\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu tr\u1ecdn b\u1ed9 qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o d\u00f9ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eeb \u00e1o, qu\u1ea7n, t\u1ea5t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ebfn 182,85 b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u fan t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 \u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0u \u00e1o s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00ea adidas thi\u1ebfu \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng khi n\u00f3 kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi trang ph\u1ee5c truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a CLB Palermo (Italia) c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Juventus t\u1eebng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc n\u00e0y c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo l\u1ecbch, M.U s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u00e1n trang ph\u1ee5c m\u00e0u h\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, M.U s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp Leicester tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4419","checkdouble":"191674"},{"date":"12:44 20/07","title":"5 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, c\u1ef1u sao MU v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/20/5-lan-chan-thuong-nang-cuu-sao-mu-van-quyet-khong-giai-nghe.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Giuseppe Rossi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Man United kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ecf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 t\u1eebng d\u00ednh 5 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i M.U, t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Villarreal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGiuseppe Rossi sinh t\u1ea1i New Jersey, M\u1ef9 trong m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh g\u1ed1c Italia. N\u0103m 12 tu\u1ed5i, anh c\u00f9ng b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Parma v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp lu\u00f4n CLB \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. 4 n\u0103m sau, Rossi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u00e1c trinh s\u00e1t vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Man United. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 Rossi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1, ra s\u00e2n 12 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a 2005/06. M\u00f9a sau \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u1ecf con nh\u01b0ng kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho Newcastle v\u00e0 Parma m\u01b0\u1ee3n, \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi 10 b\u00e0n sau 33 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Giuseppe Rossi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Giuseppe Rossi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/rossi-trong-mau-ao-Genoa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rossi t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Rossi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Villarreal sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2007. 3 m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea7u, anh l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 13, 15 v\u00e0 17 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho h\u1ecd. T\u1edbi m\u00f9a 2010/11, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Rossi n\u1edf r\u1ed9 v\u1edbi 32 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e0n ph\u00e1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111ang th\u0103ng hoa, Rossi nh\u1eadn c\u00fa s\u1ed1c. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real Madrid th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m 2011, anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, Rossi lu\u00f4n ra s\u00e2n trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng mong manh, nguy c\u01a1 ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"rossi chan thuong\" title=\"rossi chan thuong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/rossi-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rossi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, Rossi \u0111\u00e3 5 l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean b\u00e0n m\u1ed5 v\u00ec nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nan gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i. Tr\u1ea3i qua Fiorentina, Levante, Celta Vigo v\u00e0 Genoa, Rossi \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1eadt l\u1ed9n v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau m\u00f9a 2017/18, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi xa b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 hy sinh qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng&rdquo;, Rossi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t y\u00eau m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi xa n\u00f3. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ra kh\u1ecfi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9a con tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;M\u1ed7i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 bi k\u1ecbch ri\u00eang. N\u00f3 l\u1ea5y \u0111i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t World Cup, m\u1ed9t c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n m\u01a1 v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-mu-kho-long-lat-do-ngai-vang-voi-su-chuan-bi-toi-te-172-191610.html\">G\u00f3c M.U: Kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 ngai v\u00e0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/adnan-januzaj-sap-tro-lai-ngoai-hang-anh-doi-dau-mu-172-191599.html\">Adnan Januzaj s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaw-quyet-tam-quay-tro-lai-doi-hinh-chinh-mu-172-191573.html\">Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng &ldquo;d\u1eb1n m\u1eb7t&rdquo; Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rooney-phat-bieu-ve-mu-va-cuoc-dua-vo-dich-172-191513.html\">Rooney tin M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1eadt ng\u00e3 Man City m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-su-ra-di-cua-daley-blind-172-191510.html\">Mourinho c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Daley Blind?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4418","checkdouble":"191663"},{"date":"15:15 20/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 0-0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (H2): C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/20/can-tho-vs-sai-gon-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 20/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 20/7.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/can-tho-vs-sai-gon-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191671.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP C\u1ea6N TH\u01a0 VS S\u00c0I G\u00d2N</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4417","checkdouble":"191671"},{"date":"14:54 20/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Dortmund 08h05 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/20/nhan-dinh-man-city-vs-dortmund-08h05-ngay-217-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City vs Dortmund l\u00fac 08h05 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2072018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span>Man City vs Dortmund: 1-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nH\u00f4m 9/7 v\u1eeba qua, gi\u1eefa th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m World Cup v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho Man City th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. G\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong bu\u1ed5i l\u00e0m n\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 v\u1eafng v\u1ebb n\u00e0y g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 Aleks Zinchenko, Phil Foden, Brahim Diaz, Jason Denayer, Bersant Celina, Patrick Roberts v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Joe Hart. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City theo Pep sang M\u1ef9 ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u1eeb trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man xanh, nh\u00f3m nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u1ec1 t\u1ef1u theo nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ed1c th\u1eddi gian kh\u00e1c nhau. Ilkay Guendogan, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c chia tay World Cup ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u1edf v\u1ec1. Anh s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng Guardiola v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng ng\u00e0y 23/7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3 1 tu\u1ea7n, nh\u00f3m ti\u1ebfp theo g\u1ed3m Bernardo Silva (B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha), David Silva (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), Sergio Aguero v\u00e0 Nicolas Otamendi (Argentina) s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tour du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 (sau Dortmund, Man City c\u00f2n g\u1eb7p Liverpool v\u00e0 Bayern t\u1ea1i ICC).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil g\u1ed3m Fernandinho, Gabriel Jesus, Ederson v\u00e0 Danilo s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i 1 tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Man City g\u1eb7p Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh ng\u00e0y 5/8. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t cho t\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng World Cup l\u00e0 John Stones, Raheem Sterling, Fabian Delph, Raheem Sterling, Kevin De Bruyne, Vincent Kompany v\u00e0 Benjamin Mendy s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Man City s\u1ebd \u0111i du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ho\u1eb7c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Dortmund, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Austria Vienna t\u1eeb h\u00f4m 14/7. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Dortmund trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Alexander Isak. Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p Man City 1 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i ICC 2016. H\u1ecd h\u00f2a nhau 1-1 trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c (Man xanh th\u1eafng sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, do Man City kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Dortmund v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u01b0 Mario Goetze, Andre Schuerrle, Marcel Schmelzer trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, n\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00e1 cao. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Pep Guardiola th\u1eeba hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu di\u1ec5n ra sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u1edbi \u00f4ng, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Dortmund ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o Man xanh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2018/19. Trong nh\u00f3m nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fa \u00fd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng, Phil Foden. Ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh v\u00e0 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng Pep Guardiola. Hy v\u1ecdng Foden s\u1ebd t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i ICC \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\nTheo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Man City ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 3/9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Dortmund c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 2/7 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n6/8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Dortmund kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ch\u1eb5n.<br>\r\nTrong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ICC g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Man City tham d\u1ef1 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 21 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDortmund \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu 7 tr\u1eadn \u1edf 4 qu\u1ed1c gia <br>\r\nTrong khi Man City ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 3 tr\u1eadn l\u00e0m n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ICC tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh th\u00ec Dortmund t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 H\u00e8 n\u00e0y tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua t\u1edbi 7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf 4 qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c nhau. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n \u1edf Vienna (\u00c1o), sau \u0111\u00f3 sang M\u1ef9 tham d\u1ef1 ICC. R\u1eddi M\u1ef9, Dortmund l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u00c1o g\u1eb7p Rennes, sau \u0111\u00f3 sang Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Napoli. Tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Dortmund di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, v\u1edbi Lazio.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPH\u00c1T BI\u1ec2U<br>\r\nHLV Man City): &ldquo;Cho d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a H\u00e8 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Riyad Mahrez&rdquo;.<br>\r\nPep Guardiola <br>\r\nLucien Favre&nbsp; (HLV Dortmund): &ldquo;T\u00f4i vui v\u00ec ra m\u1eaft Dortmund b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Dortmund l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i HLV n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i \u0111a 1 b\u00e0n hi\u1ec7p 1<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p nhau g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa Man City v\u00e0 Dortmund, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i ICC 2016, hi\u1ec7p 1 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-bong-da/lich-thi-dau-icc-2018-ket-qua-international-champions-cup-279-190766.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 - K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 International Champions Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4416","checkdouble":"191667"},{"date":"16:40 20/07","title":"Keylor Navas kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/12/keylor-navas-khong-ngai-canh-tranh-vi-tri-voi-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Keylor Navas v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, song Real v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Thibaut Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Keylor Navas n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Keylor Navas n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Thibaut-Courtois-toi-Real-Madrid,-Keylor-Navas-noi-gi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real mua Thibaut Courtois th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra 35 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaily Mail th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Courtois \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, The Blues bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThe Blues l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-courois-172-191653.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea nh\u1eafm 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thay th\u1ebf Courtois</span>, bao g\u1ed3m Donnarumma c\u1ee7a AC Milan, Kasper Schmeichel c\u1ee7a Leicester City v\u00e0 Petr Cech c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Courtois, Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ea5t Eden Hazard v\u00e0o tay Real Madrid. C\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Keylor Navas tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Keylor Navas n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Keylor Navas n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/keylor-navas-khong-ngai-canh-tranh-vi-tri-voi-courtois.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Keylor Navas quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAS kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Navas quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ra \u0111i, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef v\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real c\u00f2n Keylor Navas kh\u00f4ng ra \u0111i, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kiko Casilla s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi b\u1edfi anh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n khi \u0111\u1ea5u khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4415","checkdouble":"191679"},{"date":"16:04 20/07","title":"Sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh NHA b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tin vui cho m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t CLB \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Everton, Tottenham hay Borussia Dortmund.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Zaha \u0111\u1eaft h\u00e0ng tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWilfried Zaha tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. Anh g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man United mua v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2013 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV David Moyes, Zaha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u. Anh b\u1ecb \u0111em cho Cardiff m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a 2013/14. Ngay sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i cho CLB c\u0169 Crystal Palace.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/15/Zaha-muon-roi-Crystal-Palace-va-tu-choi-gia-han-hop-dong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi Wilfried Zaha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n4 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, Zaha v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh gi\u00fap Palace \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Zaha l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn h\u01a1n Palace. Nh\u1eefng Everton, Tottenham hay Borussia Dortmund \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u0169i c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 m\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB n\u00e0y. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Palace \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Zaha k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 125 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng anh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Wilfried Zaha\" title=\"tien ve Wilfried Zaha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nZaha cho hay quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng. C\u1ed1t l\u00f5i l\u00e0 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n 26, Zaha tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf CLB l\u1edbn m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Zaha v\u1edbi Palace c\u00f2n t\u1edbi 4 n\u0103m v\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i. Nghe \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng NHA tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-chia-tay-sterling-172-191666.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-liverpool-danh-bai-chelsea-vu-alisson-172-191664.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1ee5 Alisson</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191654.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-courois-172-191653.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4414","checkdouble":"191673"},{"date":"17:16 20/07","title":"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sao tr\u1ebb MU sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Club America","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/mourinho-khen-ngoi-dac-biet-sao-tre-tahith-chong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 khen ng\u1ee3i sao tr\u1ebb Tahith Chong sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa Man United v\u00e0 Club America h\u00f4m nay.</h2><h2>Tahith Chong ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Juan Mata. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-1 sau khi Man United b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTahith Chong l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 Herrera b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng d\u1ed9i c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Mata s\u00fat b\u1ed3i tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Club America.</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Chong\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Tahith Chong sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Club America h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Tahith Chong sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Club America h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/mourinho-khen-ngoi-dac-biet-sao-tre-tahith-chong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Tahith Chong sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Club America</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-club-america-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191627.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Club America vs MU</span>, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man United, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 18 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTahith Chong ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. V\u00e0 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cQu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mata l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n m\u00e0 Chong \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin khi ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cD\u1eabu v\u1eady, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng khi v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n c\u00f3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t\".</em></div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMourinho l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho sao tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng Chong c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t Man United \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. B\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i \u1edf h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t c\u00f2n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 mong manh v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4413","checkdouble":"191675"},{"date":"16:13 20/07","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-alisson-toi-liverpool.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Jurgen Klopp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, song c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua sau v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua sau v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/4-nguoi-thang-va-3-nguoi-thua-sau-vu-Liverpool-mua-Alisson-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp vui m\u1eebng khi Alisson c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Mignolet ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00ec Karius l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e2m l\u00fd. S\u1ee9c \u00e9p qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1eafc 2 sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18 v\u1edbi Real Madrid khi\u1ebfn Liverpool thua 1-3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Jurgen Klopp hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o hai th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Ngay sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1 2018 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi v\u00e0 Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span>. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Kop \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng, h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung t\u1eeb Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita c\u00f2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u00eam Alisson, Liverpool h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. HLV Klopp \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson t\u1eeb Roma khi\u1ebfn hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Anfield.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loris Karius Simon Mignolet Jurgen Klopp\" title=\"Loris Karius Simon Mignolet Jurgen Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/Liverpool-chieu-mo-Alisson-Ho-da-co-De-Gea-cua-rieng-minh!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb khi Liverpool \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMignolet l\u00fac n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch ra \u0111i. Napoli \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Mignolet m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f2n v\u1edbi Karius, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 FA Cup hay c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Anh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Virgil Van Dijk v\u00e0 Dejan Lovren</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i b\u0103ng ra kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Dijk va Lovren se nhan duoc su ho tro rat lon tu Alisson\" title=\"Van Dijk v\u00e0 Lovren s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/lovren.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Van Dijk v\u00e0 Lovren s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Alisson \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Manuel Neuer c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Ederson hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City.&nbsp;V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u0103ng ra d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7&nbsp; Virgil Van Dijk v\u00e0&nbsp;Dejan Lovren.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVirgil Van Dijk th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh. V\u1edbi Dejan Lovren, anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson trong khung g\u1ed7, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m t\u1eeb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Virgil Van Dijk v\u00e0 Dejan Lovren.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Real Madrid, Don Balon th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Los Blancos \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Alisson nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u thay th\u1ebf Courtois.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"sarri\" title=\"sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hlv-sarri-chi-ra-vi-tri-yeu-nhat-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Sarri c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi HLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf Conte, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Roma. Kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alisson ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992, tuy nhi\u00ean Alisson \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Anfield thay v\u00ec Stamford Bridge. Alisson mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Klopp v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Salah thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Alisson, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Jan Oblak (Atletico Madrid) ho\u1eb7c Jasper Cillessen (Barca), song kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 The Blues c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Kasper Schmeichel</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Alisson kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Kasper Schmeichel c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kasper Schmeichel co the khoac ao Chelsea thay Courtois\" title=\"Kasper Schmeichel c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea thay Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/kas.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kasper Schmeichel c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea thay Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKasper Schmeichel n\u0103m nay 32 tu\u1ed5i, anh ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Leicester v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a 2015/16.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Leicester c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 HLV Sarri d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeicester hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao, m\u1ea5t Riyad Mahrez khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd y\u1ebfu \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Kasper Schmeichel c\u00f9ng Leicester h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Chelsea ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kasper Schmeichel, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng 3 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp The Blues \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh t\u1eeb Leicester. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 Danny Drinkwater, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa l\u00e0 Kante c\u00f2n H\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Everton</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nghe c\u00f3 v\u1ebb v\u00f4 l\u00fd b\u1edfi Everton \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu Jordan Pickford \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Everton ch\u1ecbu thua Roma trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma voi so tien thu ve tu viec ban Alisson co the vuot mat Everton vu Malcom\" title=\"Roma v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n Alisson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Everton v\u1ee5 Malcom\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/malcom.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roma v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n Alisson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Everton v\u1ee5 Malcom</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEverton \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u1ea5t trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, song m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 n\u1ebfu Roma v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoma t\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Malcom v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 40 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 Bordeaux \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thu v\u1ec1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Olympico l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Everton \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Roma v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. Theo \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Malcom mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Italia thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Roma</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2 n\u0103m 2016, Roma ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Olympico, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Wojciech Szczesny. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, khi m\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus Alisson m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Day thu mon Alisson den Liverpool, Monchi mang ve den 12 tan binh cho AS Roma he nay.\" title=\"\u0110\u1ea9y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool, Monchi mang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ebfn 12 t\u00e2n binh cho AS Roma h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/monchi-1.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb v\u1ee5 Alisson, Roma d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i khi ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, anh gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 17/37 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Serie A. T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00ean t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 80%, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoma \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Alisson cho Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 b\u00e1n anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ch\u1ec9 sau 2 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Alisson m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng n\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn 9 b\u00e0n thua trong 2 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18 v\u1edbi Liverpool.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool d\u00ednh ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa l\u1eeba th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi Roma, v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil h\u1ecd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4412","checkdouble":"191677"},{"date":"16:45 20/07","title":"Sao Chelsea nh\u1eafn nh\u1ee7 Hazard: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n anh!\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/fabregas-phat-bieu-ve-hazard-dong-doi-tai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hazard, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n anh tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEden Hazard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Anh c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p 1-0. Hazard c\u0169ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 2 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian qua, nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin Real Madrid li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Hazard ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hazard Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n anh! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hazard Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n anh! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Fabregas-phat-bieu-ve-Hazard-Chung-toi-can-anh!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea ngay sau World Cup</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00f3 tin Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt khi ngay sau World Cup, anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fabregas n\u00e0i n\u1ec9 Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n ph\u00eda l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 Hazard. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hazard cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i nh\u1eb1m ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabregas va Hazard tai chelsea\" title=\"Fabregas va Hazard tai chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/fabregas-phat-bieu-ve-hazard-dong-doi-tai-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hazard v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i d\u1ed1i, t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Hazard\u201d, Fabregas chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i CLB v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u1ea7n gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y y\u00eau m\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19 v\u00e0 Hazard c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ea5m poster qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m gia t\u0103ng ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 The Blues r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barca-doi-dembele-lay-hazard-184-191575.html\">Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 l\u1ea5y Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong-172-191562.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea: \u201cN\u1ebfu Hazard mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\">3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-quyet-dau-voi-real-vi-eden-hazard-180-191467.html\">Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real v\u00ec Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4411","checkdouble":"191678"},{"date":"09:04 20/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi c\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/dong-doi-cua-duc-chinh-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang-vi-hanh-vi-con-do.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League, trong \u0111\u00f3 ri\u00eang th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi c\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi r\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m khi \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o l\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Matias Nicolas Jadue Gonzales c\u1ee7a CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TP.H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 19/7/2018, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VFF) \u0111\u00e3 ban h\u00e0nh c\u00e1c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh\u00a0x\u1eed ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y hai m\u01b0\u01a1i tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 04 tr\u1eadn k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i V-League.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi c\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi c\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/dong-doi-cua-duc-chinh-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang-vi-hanh-vi-con-do.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 t\u1edbi 4 tr\u1eadn v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi c\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t gi\u00e0nh cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n H\u01b0ng th\u00ec l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u00f4ng\u00a0B\u00f9i Xu\u00e2n H\u00f2a c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t 5 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 02 tr\u1eadn\u00a0do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u00e0 TP.H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh. B\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf g\u1ed3m l\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Nguy\u1ec5n Minh D\u0169ng, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o vi\u00ean Nguy\u1ec5n Qu\u1ed1c H\u00f9ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M\u1ea1c \u0110\u1ee9c Vi\u1ec7t Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng th\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t sau v\u00f2ng 19 V-League l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Patiyo Tambwe c\u1ee7a XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh x\u00e2m ph\u1ea1m th\u00e2n th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Zeba Josip c\u1ee7a HAGL trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Pleiku. Patiyo s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t m\u01b0\u1eddi l\u0103m tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 03 tr\u1eadn k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, BTC tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n 70 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng do \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng trong s\u00e2n; n\u00e9m nhi\u1ec1u chai n\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u1eadt l\u1ea1 xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 ch\u1ea1y xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 mang b\u0103ng r\u00f4n c\u00f3 n\u1ed9i dung kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t 40 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng do C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u00e1c h\u00e0nh vi: \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng trong s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng; n\u00e9m nhi\u1ec1u chai n\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u1eadt l\u1ea1 xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n; ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 mang b\u0103ng r\u00f4n c\u00f3 n\u1ed9i dung kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0o s\u00e2n.\u00a0<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4410","checkdouble":"191643"}]}